edu.uidaho.junicon.runtime.junicon.iterators

Class IconVarIterator<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uidaho.junicon.runtime.junicon.iterators.IconIterator<T>
      • edu.uidaho.junicon.runtime.junicon.iterators.IconVarIterator<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IIconIterator<T>, Iterable<T>, Runnable, Callable<T>, Iterator<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IconRefIterator

    public class IconVarIterator<T>
extends IconIterator<T>
    Reified variable using closures. Need isLocal flag since Icon procedure return does not dereference unless declared local variable.

    USAGE for x : new IconVarIterator({->x}, {y->x=y})
